summaries.short: Season Two Premiere. The Miklosis have gone straight: Attila is a security guard, Janka sells cosmetics, and Mark is in college.
summaries.full: Season Two Premiere. The Miklosis have gone straight: Attila is a security guard, Janka sells cosmetics, and Mark is in college. Then Feri Gall, one of Attila's old associates, reappears, and things start going very, very wrong for the Miklosis.

summaries.short: Mira is jailed for an impulsive act of vandalism. Janka appeals to Endre to pull strings to get Mira out.
summaries.full: Mira is jailed for an impulsive act of vandalism. Janka appeals to Endre to pull strings to get Mira out. Meanwhile, Mark is expelled from college but uses some creative blackmail to try and get reinstated.

summaries.short: Season One Finale. When a situation goes south, Mark and Attila team up to save themselves.
summaries.full: Season One Finale. When a situation goes south, Mark and Attila team up to save themselves. Meanwhile, Janka must choose between her lover and her family. Is blood really thicker than water for the Miklosis?

summaries.short: Janka leaves Attila for Endre and takes the kids with her. Feri exerts covert pressure on Endre.
summaries.full: Janka leaves Attila for Endre and takes the kids with her. Feri exerts covert pressure on Endre, and Attila and Mira get caught in the middle. What sacrifices will Attila make to spare his child?

summaries.full: Attila confronts Endre but faces a tough choice as to how to avenge his son. Mark is arrested and pressured to give up Endre. Mira plans to go abroad; Janka lives the life of her dreams.
